
[XXX] To install LLVM 3.4.2
http://llvm.org/docs/GettingStarted.html

[XXX] To install whole-program-llvm
https://github.com/travitch/whole-program-llvm
$ git clone https://github.com/travitch/whole-program-llvm.git
(For Ubuntu 10.04 where python 2.6.xx does not have argparse)
$ sudo apt-get install python-argparse

[XXX] To install Neongoby
$ git clone https://github.com/columbia/neongoby.git
$ cd [NEONGOBY_HOME]
$ git submodule init
$ git submodule update
$ ./configure --prefix=`llvm-config --prefix`
$ make
$ make install

[XXX] To install PIN

download and install - https://software.intel.com/en-us/articles/pintool-downloads


